articles.title: ASEAN struggles for unity on Myanmar conflict - Reuters
articles.description: Finding unity over how to deal with Myanmar's junta continued to evade Southeast Asian nations on Thursday, as foreign ministers meeting in Jakarta struggled to agree on a communique that would include a reference to their neighbour's internal strife.
